import React from "react";
import { Container, Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap";
import Navigation from "../Component/Navigation";
import "./Style.css"
import {FaFacebookSquare} from "react-icons/fa"
import {BsInstagram , BsTwitter} from "react-icons/bs"

const About = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Row>
        <Navigation />
      </Row>
      <Row>
        <Col className="about-background mt-5">
          <Container>
            <Row> Name - Aatish</Row>
            <Row>
               Contact Us-
                
            </Row>
            <Row>
                <Col><FaFacebookSquare/></Col>
                <Col><BsInstagram/></Col>
                <Col><BsTwitter/></Col>
                <Col><BsLinkedin/></Col>
            </Row>
          </Container>
        </Col>
        <Col className="about-background mt-5 ml-5">
          <Container>
            <Row> Name - Ritu Kumari</Row>
            <Row>
               Contact Us-
                
            </Row>
            <Row>
                <Col><FaFacebookSquare/></Col>
                <Col><BsInstagram/></Col>
                <Col><BsTwitter/></Col>
                <Col><BsLinkedin/></Col>
            </Row>
          </Container>
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </>
  );
};
export default About;
